headline: Al Qimmah and Marriott to develop five new hotels in Saudi Arabia
summary: The agreement includes JW Marriott Jeddah, The Apartments, which will be located on Jeddah Corniche Road.

headline: Hilton, Marriott, and Hyatt Are Near Record Highs. These 2 Hotel Stocks Are Better Buys.
summary: Shares of premium hotels get premium valuations, but lower-end chains could benefit from the World Cup and other events.
